name: Alpha Five Project Properties File
summary: Properties file created by Alpha Five, an IDE that enables users to develop mobile, desktop, and Web applications; contains properties for a project; includes the project style, allowed filenames, JavaScript libraries, CSS libraries, and Email settings; referenced by Alpha Five, not meant to be manually opened; located in the "WebProject" folder of the project along with the .SECURITYSETTINGS file.

open.note: Open with an associated app listed below.
